'''潛水表'''（Diver's watch）是強化耐水性能的[[手錶|手錶]]中，主要用於[[潛水|潛水]]等高水壓環境作業時使用的手錶<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.watchtime.com/blog/dive-watch-wednesday-what-did-divers-use-before-dive-watches/ |title=What Did Divers Use Before Dive Watches? By Roger Ruegger, WatchTime.com, May 2014 |access-date=2015-10-09 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092352/https://www.watchtime.com/blog/dive-watch-wednesday-what-did-divers-use-before-dive-watches/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。潛水表的國際規格是ISO 6425:1996，而一般用耐水表的工業規格是ISO 2281/JIS B 7021。潛水表要求能經受至少100米的潛水及相當於水下100米處1.25倍的水壓，並且還要求具有夜光功能以在水下也能確認時間。

